Description
-----------

Controls which image to blend a [visportals](Visportal "Visportal") to when it's closing.

Usage
-----

In the global section of your material shader type...

    portalImage [map]

Parameters
----------

-   [map] - the relative path and file name to the specified portal image.

Notes
-----

Usually the image used is "\_black". See also the [portaldistancefar](Portaldistancefar_%28Material_global_keyword%29 "Portaldistancefar (Material global keyword)") and [portaldistancenear](Portaldistancenear_%28Material_global_keyword%29 "Portaldistancenear (Material global keyword)") keywords.

